name: CryptoSushis - Reborn and Ready to Roll

metadata.name: DessertSushi Shiba #51 #1/9
metadata.description: Treat yourself to the charming Shiba-inspired sushi, a sweet sensation for Shiba enthusiasts. Enveloped in strawberry jelly, it holds velvety vanilla ice cream within. Garnished with strawberries, raspberries, and blueberries, the colorful Shiba logo takes center stage with a fruity jelly core. A truly irresistible delight!
